Exam Killer - AI Study Assistant

A Python-based Micro-SaaS prototype built with Streamlit and Google Generative AI SDK.

How it works:

Ingestion: Parses PDF documents using pypdf to extract raw text.

Processing: Sends structured prompts to the Gemini LLM to generate valid JSON output.

State Management: Utilizes Streamlit's session_state to handle quiz persistence and user interactions without page reloads.

UI/UX: dynamic interface for taking the quiz and reviewing scores.

Tech Stack: Python 3.10+, Streamlit, Google Gemini API, PyPDF.
